channel.description: I just listened to The black parade (out on 23-24th) I personally prefered Three Cheers For Sweet Revenge (2004 - mcr) But i did enjoy listening to the black parade, some songs were plain boring but my favorite song was called teenagers anyways i recomend people download it, or buy it, if you can... comments :-
